#########################################
### TIPOS DE INSTITUCIÓN
#########################################

### Registrar Tipo de Institución - Universidad
POST {{baseUrl}}/institution-types
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Universidad"
}

### Registrar Tipo de Institución - Empresa
POST {{baseUrl}}/institution-type
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Empresa"
}

### Obtener Todos los Tipos de Institución
GET {{baseUrl}}/institution-type
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener Tipo de Institución por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/institution-type/{{institutionTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Actualizar Tipo de Institución
PUT {{baseUrl}}/institution-type/{{institutionTypeId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Universidad Pública"
}

### Eliminar (Dar de Baja) Tipo de Institución
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/institution-type/{{institutionTypeId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

